{"tid":760672,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坤哥邊個chok樣型仔d？😁","createTime":"2018-07-29T17:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T11:31:18.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"566d95f8419318e2f8afea5ffd9d8fc580545979","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:33:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#1</span> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com/vp/3cb2d52363b30c6a701fa4c60aca8fe9/5BD7090C/t51.2885-15/e35/37801921_246661042725431_5498003814751404032_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F3cb2d52363b30c6a701fa4c60aca8fe9%2F5BD7090C%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F37801921_246661042725431_5498003814751404032_n.jpg&h=6c314d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n定......"},{"pid":"b362e44c6dc393ebde70be79740c4397fa04face","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:33:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#2</span> 呢 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com/vp/225fb1b9943779484c04724ac4e0c52b/5C12DA89/t51.2885-15/e35/33020502_1753727961384491_3437233718211641344_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F225fb1b9943779484c04724ac4e0c52b%2F5C12DA89%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F33020502_1753727961384491_3437233718211641344_n.jpg&h=d6df61a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a99017b4dcf75da3de1a8512ace8d638a18b8ca0","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://yahoo-promotion.myguide.hk/tumblr/refine/_vol10/images/_share/fb_share.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyahoo-promotion.myguide.hk%2Ftumblr%2Frefine%2F_vol10%2Fimages%2F_share%2Ffb_share.jpg&h=6d1dd9b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據2007年由網民編製的「毒男計分表」，當代年輕男性具備以下生活特徵；嚴重缺乏自信、欠缺穿衣品味、怯於約會女性、不擅辭令、甚至沉迷打電玩等，皆可被歸類為「中毒過深」。然而，這些看似會讓女生「走夾唔抖」的趕客特質，卻竟然讓吳業坤將之轉化成親和力極高、甚至是異性緣極其旺盛的毒男異數，一眾大感葡萄的網民更索性為坤哥冠以「偽毒」稱號，以洩心頭之憤。"},{"pid":"34f049c309cfb0b7fdb85100f4e2ac02cb5bf5e2","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://yahoo-promotion.myguide.hk/tumblr/refine/_vol10/images/img-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyahoo-promotion.myguide.hk%2Ftumblr%2Frefine%2F_vol10%2Fimages%2Fimg-2.jpg&h=50d01259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>究竟，「偽毒」是「毒男」的代名詞，還是進階版？</em>"},{"pid":"60f2363a4451c296d98efa5277716a11d8267608","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://yahoo-promotion.myguide.hk/tumblr/refine/_vol10/images/img-portrait-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyahoo-promotion.myguide.hk%2Ftumblr%2Frefine%2F_vol10%2Fimages%2Fimg-portrait-1.jpg&h=8dfae7ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12376fccd8254b756ba9a41ff6ba02137a0900de","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://yahoo-promotion.myguide.hk/tumblr/refine/_vol10/images/_svg/img-title-4.svg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyahoo-promotion.myguide.hk%2Ftumblr%2Frefine%2F_vol10%2Fimages%2F_svg%2Fimg-title-4.svg&h=9b8d65ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n很多人認為「脫毒」是剪個柏豪頭，把格仔恤衫丟棄，做gym操肌穿上A&amp;F貼身tee；在坤哥身上的「脫毒」卻是內心的成熟，以及對喜歡的事情的堅持，並且擁有「我是偽毒，又如何？」的坦白。「偽毒最能形容真正的我。我覺得偽毒這個詞語很獨特，是近一兩年才興起的詞語，用來形容外表與內在不成正比的人。」讓他選最能形容自己的詞語，坤哥毫不猶豫就從男神、暖男、毒男和偽毒這四個潮語中，選出偽毒一詞。他說自己當初參加《超級巨星2》時是真．毒男一名，後來加入TVB令他學會獨立、學會爭取，才由毒男進階為偽毒。正如他自己所說：「坤哥披著毒男的外表，但其實內心會思考很多東西。入行頭兩年我還在讀書，所以把TVB當成一份part time看待；不過當我畢業後，就不得不開始思考，是否要把演藝工作當成自己的終身職業。」認真思考後的坤哥，開始在主持和拍劇的同時，在網上唱cover，他的Youtube Channel - Kwan Gor至今擁有超過13萬訂閱。簡單地做自己喜歡的事，想不到竟被他殺出一條血路，在網絡上紅起來。"},{"pid":"dfc9dc6b056f368771c9285958b6ace40d25b4bf","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://yahoo-promotion.myguide.hk/tumblr/refine/_vol10/images/_svg/img-title-3.svg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyahoo-promotion.myguide.hk%2Ftumblr%2Frefine%2F_vol10%2Fimages%2F_svg%2Fimg-title-3.svg&h=91486cf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n很多人認為「脫毒」是剪個柏豪頭，把格仔恤衫丟棄，做gym操肌穿上A&amp;F貼身tee；在坤哥身上的「脫毒」卻是內心的成熟，以及對喜歡的事情的堅持，並且擁有「我是偽毒，又如何？」的坦白。「偽毒最能形容真正的我。我覺得偽毒這個詞語很獨特，是近一兩年才興起的詞語，用來形容外表與內在不成正比的人。」讓他選最能形容自己的詞語，坤哥毫不猶豫就從男神、暖男、毒男和偽毒這四個潮語中，選出偽毒一詞。他說自己當初參加《超級巨星2》時是真．毒男一名，後來加入TVB令他學會獨立、學會爭取，才由毒男進階為偽毒。正如他自己所說：「坤哥披著毒男的外表，但其實內心會思考很多東西。入行頭兩年我還在讀書，所以把TVB當成一份part time看待；不過當我畢業後，就不得不開始思考，是否要把演藝工作當成自己的終身職業。」認真思考後的坤哥，開始在主持和拍劇的同時，在網上唱cover，他的Youtube Channel - Kwan Gor至今擁有超過13萬訂閱。簡單地做自己喜歡的事，想不到竟被他殺出一條血路，在網絡上紅起來。"},{"pid":"855d97e7ca60cfe848fc2409627a25b864dd6c22","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:54:34.000Z","msg":"從前，在電視機中出現的歌手才是主流；現在，在網絡上大大小小Youtuber，才是新世代心中的「主流」。今日的男神不像當年的偶像一般離地三千呎，而是，更貼地的、可以在facebook上互留comment的、有來有往的一種更像是同 伴的存在。<br />\n當偶像變成男神，黎明由風流倜儻的原振俠，變成「習慣空肚食早餐」的金句王。坤哥的起步點是大台的巨星幫，再轉戰到網絡新．主流Youtuber，無心插柳下，竟登上本地樂壇最具公信力的叱咤。由主流飄到新主流，最後強勢回歸主流，坤哥在各類媒體中都凝聚了一群粉絲，不知不覺升格到大眾心中的男神級別。坤哥說：「其實我覺得男神，即是偶像的意思吧。好似以前我媽咪會講黎明係我偶像，而不會用男神這個字。」"},{"pid":"01cec9effa5b28d6a1fa8f51242e9498d023543b","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://yahoo-promotion.myguide.hk/tumblr/refine/_vol10/images/img-portrait-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyahoo-promotion.myguide.hk%2Ftumblr%2Frefine%2F_vol10%2Fimages%2Fimg-portrait-2.jpg&h=0375e02d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41895775dec5bfcb397459b45aefa403d3106dbd","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://yahoo-promotion.myguide.hk/tumblr/refine/_vol10/images/_svg/img-title-5.svg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyahoo-promotion.myguide.hk%2Ftumblr%2Frefine%2F_vol10%2Fimages%2F_svg%2Fimg-title-5.svg&h=57276571&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網絡世界中的男神，曬OOTD、咖啡紅酒、名車靚錶。不是Chok樣，就是騷人魚線，像活在玻璃球中的樣辦公仔，煞是好看，卻離地。活躍於社交網絡的坤哥卻展現出不一樣的生活感，一不小心把「食好東西」寫成了「食好西」，造就坤哥的經典facebook status，同時也令「#食好西」變為網絡關鍵字。「偽毒」貼地的錯誤，令人覺得可笑又可愛。「於我來說，social media是用來分享自己最真摯的東西的地方。當然會分享工作，但是也會分享工作以外的東西。」社交媒體叫人又愛又恨，網民既能捧紅你，也可以踩死你。社交媒體中的坤哥形象異常立體，不時會與網民互動，抽水食花生又或是自嘲派膠瓣瓣齊，難道不會擔心被攻擊？畢竟網絡上道德L與hater從不缺少，坤哥淡然說不會太擔心，「我覺得只要相信自己的立場，說甚麼都可以。世上沒有絕對的對與錯，不應太緊張別人的說話和評論。如果有人惡意攻擊我，我通常都不會回覆，卻也不會刪除留言，就讓其他人一同討論，自然會有正反立場出現。」"},{"pid":"4bee96db5e96db4f06b2e1cbdb760f55bc6ce52b","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://yahoo-promotion.myguide.hk/tumblr/refine/_vol10/images/_svg/img-title-6.svg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyahoo-promotion.myguide.hk%2Ftumblr%2Frefine%2F_vol10%2Fimages%2F_svg%2Fimg-title-6.svg&h=d9a86292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一般人心中的男神要集齊三高：身高、學歷高，以及收入高。沒有這三高，動輒被標籤為廢青，但在「偽毒」坤哥心目中，廢青並不廢，「其實做人，是否一定要做大眾心中的最top？難道不可以擁有自己的一片天地嗎？我覺得就算被人稱為廢青也不用氣餒，只要能找到自己的價值就可以。像我知道自己不是做靚仔的材料，所以不會為了做偶像派而除下眼鏡、減廿磅，這樣，反而會迷失了自我。」拒絕隨波逐流、拒絕被世俗所規範，「我認為每個人都是獨特的，做回真正的自己，才是最重要。」就像坤哥最新派台歌《百姓》中所講「安份做百姓／擇個時辰／翻身躍起」腳踏實地，默默寸進，想的足夠透徹的話，你會明白，平凡人其實絕不平凡。簡單的處世之道，卻是太陽底下的大智慧。誰敢說「偽毒」是庸才？"},{"pid":"a270b7e7593e83d2be534f6fc29058f4258449f1","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/014602_21d40944c82c7037743c25343320d45d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F014602_21d40944c82c7037743c25343320d45d.jpg&h=44b774a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d9606baeb6474944f7c58c9a10f6c4a61696629","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:57:19.000Z","msg":"好文好文我like左！ <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f316e2a3f5261540488b6af8b691e8c4d4d0e4cd","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T19:44:58.000Z","msg":"大塊田係咪同佢最熟？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b15b8839370a34e4672620cbcc1ca387fcad7593","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T20:07:22.000Z","msg":"中伏！田蕊妮畀吳業坤老點跣鑊甘<br />\n<br />\n07月29日(日) 22:45<br />\n<br />\n田蕊妮（阿田）與吳業坤為《流行經典50年》錄影，他們將會推出合唱歌，但阿田笑言覺得被對方「老點」：「佢有日打畀我話Wyman（黃偉文）提議我哋合唱，我心諗Wyman提議得梗係好，佢好多諗頭，但事後我發現係吳業坤提議。」吳業坤解釋指Wyman問他有沒有對象可以擺上枱，他即時想起阿田。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"d7bbc9481a3205560fab407987f52b601f8cec36","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T20:07:47.000Z","msg":"唔敢同阿田拍親熱戲&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提到新歌講姐弟戀，兩人坦言錄音時才知，阿田又指錄音當日吳業坤特登去錄音室騷擾她：「佢笑口咁問我係咪好後悔，覺得自己瀨嘢，我喺呢行都算有經驗，我畀佢兜口兜面咁跣咗一鑊。不過其實係值得，好玩嘅。」吳業坤笑言阿田會因該合唱歌而名留青史，成為香港樂壇上一個印記。他又透露有計劃拍MV，承諾會拍到阿田美麗、動人又大方：「阿田畀咗個提議，個MV可以係宅男幻想一個女神去打救佢，保護我呢個小弟弟。（會唔會有親熱鏡頭？）唔會。（驚阿田老公杜汶澤？）都驚，少少啦！佢係黑帶，再加埋佢依家個身形就多多驚，所以都係藝術成分重少少，唔好太關注肉體，不過我都好鍾意阿田嘅內衣廣告，好正，田蕊妮好正，身材好。」"},{"pid":"44d3021c132aa85ffeab6e5c857529e591d730cc","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T20:08:44.000Z","msg":"再唱經典&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿田透露會在節目中獻唱兩首對她來說十分經典的歌曲，分別是《一首獨唱的歌》與《沒那麼簡單》，她說：「我1993年參加唱歌比賽時，就係唱《一首獨唱的歌》贏得冠軍而入行，但之後一直冇做過同音樂有關嘅工作，喺我覺得同音樂距離愈嚟愈遠，喺我入年20後，終於有機會出唱片，係翻唱歌嘅唱片，入面就翻唱咗《沒那麼簡單》。」阿田稱已很久未有在電視節目上現場唱歌，加上其父親到了現場捧場，令她有點緊張：「我爸爸對我唱歌方面好挑剔，從來冇喺佢口中聽過話滿意我嘅表現。」"},{"pid":"85027a5250bcdf57f549811506a041dd5316cc46","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:36:18.000Z","msg":"牙坤!!!!!!!!!!<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/072338_8552a494fb26c671de7a260ecdc13af3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F072338_8552a494fb26c671de7a260ecdc13af3.png&h=c332d91f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f2c6925d860a9f97b302bc8956f31022361d021","tid":760672,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:00:24.000Z","msg":"張張都咁型棍子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d56c23e7b9d299002c979fdf5442245b9e1590","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:38:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張張都咁型棍子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認同<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75ab5ed6f2476fde8863d109fb9f9886616dba9b","tid":760672,"uid":75426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"Kwangor 360度無死角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c376888495c1706c9896aa759236161b618a93","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T04:48:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Kwangor 360度無死角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好型！<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f512ae98893541782cc5704c89b99c1ccd8d2497","tid":760672,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"百 變 chok 樣 坤 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/005845_c419fadd0143d63f831f350722137954.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F005845_c419fadd0143d63f831f350722137954.png&h=4e576bb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26943131e70ea3bf672966a529d59b1294aee947","tid":760672,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:20:28.000Z","msg":"電視藝人嚟講算樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f902ae60e35ee707b1c8034df82c5af4d4f9be3b","tid":760672,"uid":129221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"I ❤️坤哥"}]}